Margery Wilson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Margery_Wilson 0 Margery Wilson (October 31, 1896 – January 21, 1986), was an American actress, writer, and silent movie director. She appeared in 51 films between 1914 and 1939. Wilson was born in Gracey, Kentucky and died in Arcadia, California.
